import Bg1 from '../assets/images/marketers_hero_img2.png';
import Bg2 from '../assets/images/svg-2.svg';
import Bg3 from '../assets/images/profile.jpg';
import Bg4 from '../assets/images/svg-3.svg';

export const homeObjOne = {
    primary: true,
    lightBg: false,
    lightTopLine: true,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    // topLine: 'Instant Setup',
    headline: 'Placing your business on every screen',
    description:
      'In our world there\'s nothing like competition, we place you at the peak of the market.',
    buttonLabel: 'Get Started',
    imgStart: '',
    img: `${Bg1}`,
    alt: 'Credit Card',
    start: ''
  };
  
  export const homeObjTwo = {
    primary: true,
    lightBg: false,
    lightTopLine: true,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: 'How It Works',
    headline: 'Extremely quick onboarding process',
    description:
      "Once you've joined, our team of specialist will reach out to you and get you set up in minutes.",
    buttonLabel: 'Learn More',
    imgStart: '',
    img: `${Bg2}`,
    alt: 'Vault',
    start: ''
  };
  
  export const homeObjThree = {
    primary: false,
    lightBg: true,
    lightTopLine: false,
    lightText: false,
    lightTextDesc: false,
    topLine: 'Chinazo Ibe',
    headline:
      'Peakprime helped me increase my revenue by over 3X in less than 3 months!',
    description:
      "Their team is wonderful! I can't believe I didn't start working with them earlier.",
    buttonLabel: 'View Case Study',
    imgStart: 'start',
    img: `${Bg3}`,
    alt: 'Vault',
    start: 'true'
  };
  
  export const homeObjFour = {
    primary: true,
    lightBg: false,
    lightTopLine: true,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: 'Secure Database',
    headline: 'All your data is stored on our secure server',
    description:
      'You will never have to worry about your information getting leaked. Our team of security experts will ensure your records are kept safe.',
    buttonLabel: 'Sign Up Now',
    imgStart: 'start',
    img: `${Bg4}`,
    alt: 'Vault',
    start: 'true'
  };
